    "It should be possible to perform such task using a logit model or a RNN model, if trained and designed for such purpose.",
    "This alternative approach will require a large amount of data.",
    "This burden is overcome using the pre-trained Transformer model.",
    "Nevertheless, it would be important to confirm the accuracy and usability of such approaches.",
    "Lastly, we suggest the application of the proposed approach to different languages."
